reviewText: Too  bad she did not have a better career.  Her music is OUTSTANDING.
Julie Roberts is a class act. Her deep bluesy voice shows in this dvd. Julie Roberts is or should take country music by storm.
Julie Roberts showed in this video why she was up to the task of being a country performer in the highest regard.

This is a very warm story of Julie Roberts journey into the music business. Promoting a new song is the key to any brand-new artist success, so the long days and nights, and endless miles on the road is part of Julie's life.  It show's how hard it is to break into the music industry. You can have a tremendous amount of talent, and still there is this constant battle to have your song played over the radio air wave. There are hundreds of songs waging this action each week.
  This video also shows the courage, and personality she obtains. Julie's sense of humor is adorable, and shows how much of a real individual she is.
